text: “Houdini” is a 2023 song by English-Albanian singer Dua Lipa. It was released on , and will appear on her third album. The song has been successful on the charts, reaching number two in the UK. A music video for the song was released at the same time, featuring Lipa dancing in a dance studio. == References == == Other websites == * Category:2023 songs Category:Dua Lipa songs
